  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational epidemiologic multicentric study of follow-up a cohort for described
      the situation of patients with primary ovarian insufficiency in public population with
      respect to the age of apparition the primary ovarian insufficiency .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
